</span><span class="line"><span class="w">        </span><span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">]</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></div>
</figure>

<p>Now we assign our <span class="keycombo separated" title="J"><kbd class="key symbol">J</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="I"><kbd class="key symbol">I</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="K"><kbd class="key symbol">K</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="L"><kbd class="key symbol">L</kbd></span> keys to
<span class="keycombo separated" title="Left Arrow Key"><kbd class="key symbol">&#8592;</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="Up Arrow Key"><kbd class="key symbol">&#8593;</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="Down Arrow Key"><kbd class="key symbol">&#8595;</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="Right Arrow Key"><kbd class="key symbol">&#8594;</kbd></span> when pressed along
with the <span class="keycombo separated" title="Semicolon"><kbd class="key symbol">;</kbd></span> key (which is now Left-<span class="keycombo separated" title="Function-Command"><kbd class="mod symbol">Fn</kbd><span class="keycombo combiner">+</span><kbd class="mod symbol">&#8984;</kbd></span>).</p>

<blockquote class="tip">
  <p>To make this into <span class="keycombo separated" title="H"><kbd class="key symbol">H</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="J"><kbd class="key symbol">J</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="K"><kbd class="key symbol">K</kbd></span><span class="keycombo separator">/</span><span class="keycombo separated" title="L"><kbd class="key symbol">L</kbd></span> navigation, change the
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">"key_code": "k"</code> lines to h, j, k, and l, in that order.</p>
</blockquote>

